        <article>
          Jaff is an experienced and visionary leader in the conservation and
          tourism industry, serving as the Owner and Director of Tazama Africa.
          With a decade of experience in the field, Jaff has always been driven
          by a passion to create exceptional travel experiences that have a
          positive impact on the environment and local communities in Tanzania.
        </article>
        <p>
          Inspired by his deep commitment to conservation and sustainability,
          Jaff founded Tazama Africa with the vision of providing travelers with
          unique and authentic journeys that respect and celebrate the natural
          beauty and cultural heritage of the region. Under his guidance, the
          company has become renowned for its innovative and socially
          responsible approach to travel, earning Jaff a reputation as a true
          pioneer in the industry.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through his leadership and unwavering dedication, Jaff has
          successfully built a thriving travel company that not only delivers
          unforgettable experiences for visitors, but also creates fair
          employment opportunities for Tanzanians and helps
          protecttheenvironmentforfuturegenerations
        </p>
      </section>

      <h3
        class="py-4 cursor-pointer bg-[#98866E] shadow-xl w-full text-white text-center uppercase tracking-wide mt-5"
