        <article>
          Tazama Africa creates unforgettable travel experiences that are
          environmentally sustainable and culturally sensitive. With over a
          decade of experience in the safari business, we partner with local
          outfitters to provide authentic and responsible trips that benefit
          small businesses and the communities they serve
        </article>
        <article>
          Our passionate guides and staff ensure that your journey is seamless
          from start to finish. We're committed to fair wages and investing in
          our employees for the long term. We also believe in inspiring the next
          generation of conservationists, partnering with local organizations to
          bring Tanzanian youth into national parks to learn about ecology and
          wildlife conservation.
        </article>
        <p>
          At Tazama Africa, we're dedicated to reducing waste and using
          low-impact business practices. By choosing to travel with us, you're
          choosing to travel responsibly and contribute to positive impact in
